OL,3,CMan, 36, remanded into custody after
OL,4,Cseven people hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FA man has been remanded into custody
OL,7,Fafter appearing at court after seven
OL,8,Fpeople were injured when a car hit
OL,9,Fpedestrians in Derby.
OL,11,FSandhu Ponnachan, 36, of Chariot
OL,12,FClose, Alvaston, appeared at Southern
OL,13,FDerbyshire Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FWednesday (April 1st), accused of
OL,15,Fdangerous driving.
OL,17,FHe was also charged with six counts of
OL,18,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,19,Fintent, one count of attempted
OL,20,Fgrievous bodily harm, and one count of
OL,21,Fpossession of a bladed article.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
