OL,3,CMan, 36, remanded into custody after
OL,4,Cseven people hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FSeven people were injured, some
OL,7,Fseriously, outside the Bishop Blaise
OL,8,Fpub in Friar Gate at around 9.30pm on
OL,9,FSaturday when a black Suzuki Swift
OL,10,Fmounted the pavement.
OL,12,FThe victims were four men and three
OL,13,Fwomen aged between 36 and 52, and four
OL,14,Fhave been discharged from hospital,
OL,15,FDerbyshire Police said.
OL,17,FPonnachan, who is originally from
OL,18,FIndia but now lives in Derby, was
OL,19,Farrested seven minutes after the
OL,20,Fincident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
