OL,3,CMan, 36, remanded into custody after
OL,4,Cseven people hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FAppearing in the dock at the
OL,7,Fmagistrates' court, Ponnachan showed
OL,8,Fno emotion.
OL,10,FHe was wearing glasses and dressed in
OL,11,Fa plain grey T-shirt, grey jogging
OL,12,Fbottom and light blue croc-type
OL,13,Ffootwear, spoke only to confirm his
OL,14,Fpersonal details, including his
OL,15,Faddress.
OL,17,FThe 36-year-old was remanded in
OL,18,Fcustody until an appearance at Derby
OL,19,FCrown Court on April 29.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
