OL,3,CMan, 36, remanded into custody after
OL,4,Cseven people hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FThere was no application for bail
OL,7,Fduring the hearing, which lasted for
OL,8,Faround five minutes.
OL,10,FDistrict Judge Jonathan Taaffe began
OL,11,Fthe hearing by addressing Ponnachan
OL,12,Fdirectly.
OL,14,FThe judge told him: "You face a number
OL,15,Fof charges from an incident on March
OL,16,F28th.
