OL,3,CMan, 36, remanded into custody after
OL,4,Cseven people hit by car in Derby
OL,6,F"It's said that upon that date you
OL,7,Fdrove dangerously and that you
OL,8,Fcommitted acts that have unlawfully
OL,9,Fand maliciously caused grievous bodily
OL,10,Fharm to a number of people.
OL,12,F"Given the nature of the charges, they
OL,13,Fcan only be dealt with at the Crown
OL,14,FCourt."
